      "text": [
        " قَالَ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"لاَ تَجُوزُ شَهَادَةٌ عَلَى شَهَادَةٍ فِي حَدٍّ وَ لاَ كَفَالَةٌ فِي حَدٍّ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3356 - Ghiyath ibn Ibrahim narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as):\nImam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said: \"Testimony upon testimony is not valid in cases involving prescribed punishments (hudud), nor is sponsorship (kafalah) valid in cases involving prescribed punishments.\""
        ]
      }
    },
